cs.CR, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.SE

The paper deals with the problem of protecting real-time UAV applications against DoS attacks, which is a security issue (cs.CR). The proposed framework is designed to provide resilient control for real-time UAV systems, which involves robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The framework also involves communication channels, which falls under networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Finally, the paper presents a software implementation of the framework, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE).
